{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1412,"text":"So, I'm afraid."},{"time":3618,"text":"Right now,"},{"time":5096,"text":"on this stage,"},{"time":6641,"text":"I feel fear."},{"time":9099,"text":"In my life, I ain't met many people"},{"time":10826,"text":"that will readily admit\nwhen they are afraid."},{"time":13598,"text":"And I think that's because deep down,"},{"time":15665,"text":"they know how easy it spreads."},{"time":18468,"text":"See, fear is like a disease."},{"time":20912,"text":"When it moves, it moves like wildfire."},{"time":23912,"text":"But what happens when,"},{"time":25514,"text":"even in the face of that fear,"},{"time":27288,"text":"you do what you've got to do?"},{"time":29294,"text":"That's called courage."},{"time":31354,"text":"And just like fear,"},{"time":33061,"text":"courage is contagious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":35870,"text":"See, I'm from East St. Louis, Illinois."},{"time":38143,"text":"That's a small city"},{"time":39327,"text":"across the Mississippi River\nfrom St. Louis, Missouri."},{"time":42165,"text":"I have lived in and around\nSt. Louis my entire life."},{"time":48443,"text":"When Michael Brown, Jr.,"},{"time":49771,"text":"an ordinary teenager,"},{"time":51047,"text":"was gunned down by police in 2014\nin Ferguson, Missouri --"},{"time":55621,"text":"another suburb, but north of St. Louis --"},{"time":58804,"text":"I remember thinking,"},{"time":60361,"text":"he ain't the first,"},{"time":62144,"text":"and he won't be the last young kid\nto lose his life to law enforcement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66488,"text":"But see, his death was different."},{"time":69065,"text":"When Mike was killed,"},{"time":70412,"text":"I remember the powers that be\ntrying to use fear as a weapon."},{"time":75180,"text":"The police response to a community\nin mourning was to use force"},{"time":78732,"text":"to impose fear:"},{"time":80744,"text":"fear of militarized police,"},{"time":82913,"text":"imprisonment,"},{"time":84166,"text":"fines."},{"time":85359,"text":"The media even tried\nto make us afraid of each other"},{"time":87903,"text":"by the way they spun the story."},{"time":89479,"text":"And all of these things\nhave worked in the past."},{"time":91862,"text":"But like I said,\nthis time it was different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95664,"text":"Michael Brown's death and the subsequent\ntreatment of the community"},{"time":99062,"text":"led to a string of protests in and around\nFerguson and St. Louis."},{"time":103560,"text":"When I got out to those protests\nabout the fourth or fifth day,"},{"time":107349,"text":"it was not out of courage;"},{"time":109367,"text":"it was out of guilt."},{"time":111495,"text":"See, I'm black."},{"time":113223,"text":"I don't know if y'all noticed that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114992,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116041,"text":"But I couldn't sit in St. Louis,\nminutes away from Ferguson,"},{"time":121542,"text":"and not go see."},{"time":123035,"text":"So I got off my ass to go check it out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125501,"text":"When I got out there,"},{"time":126965,"text":"I found something surprising."},{"time":130650,"text":"I found anger; there was a lot of that."},{"time":133507,"text":"But what I found more of was love."},{"time":136745,"text":"People with love for themselves."},{"time":138677,"text":"Love for their community."},{"time":140341,"text":"And it was beautiful --"},{"time":142054,"text":"until the police showed up."},{"time":144675,"text":"Then a new emotion was interjected\ninto the conversation:"},{"time":148995,"text":"fear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150627,"text":"Now, I'm not going to lie;"},{"time":152336,"text":"when I saw those armored vehicles,"},{"time":155154,"text":"and all that gear"},{"time":156339,"text":"and all those guns"},{"time":157729,"text":"and all those police"},{"time":159514,"text":"I was terrified --"},{"time":161001,"text":"personally."},{"time":163971,"text":"And when I looked around that crowd,"},{"time":165749,"text":"I saw a lot of people that had\nthe same thing going on."},{"time":168535,"text":"But I also saw people\nwith something else inside of them."},{"time":172230,"text":"That was courage."},{"time":173847,"text":"See, those people yelled,"},{"time":175249,"text":"and they screamed,"},{"time":176515,"text":"and they were not about\nto back down from the police."},{"time":179091,"text":"They were past that point."},{"time":180763,"text":"And then I could feel\nsomething in me changing,"},{"time":183038,"text":"so I yelled and I screamed,"},{"time":185489,"text":"and I noticed that everybody around me\nwas doing the same thing."},{"time":189827,"text":"And there was nothing like that feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193023,"text":"So I decided I wanted\nto do something more."},{"time":195605,"text":"I went home, I thought:\nI'm an artist. I make shit."},{"time":198933,"text":"So I started making things\nspecific to the protest,"},{"time":204092,"text":"things that would be weapons\nin a spiritual war,"},{"time":208437,"text":"things that would give people voice"},{"time":211471,"text":"and things that would fortify them\nfor the road ahead."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215054,"text":"I did a project where I took pictures\nof the hands of protesters"},{"time":218491,"text":"and put them up and down\nthe boarded-up buildings"},{"time":222505,"text":"and community shops."},{"time":224870,"text":"My goal was to raise awareness\nand to raise the morale."},{"time":228514,"text":"And I think, for a minute at least,"},{"time":230939,"text":"it did just that."},{"time":233950,"text":"Then I thought, I want to uplift\nthe stories of these people"},{"time":237514,"text":"I was watching being\ncourageous in the moment."},{"time":240438,"text":"And myself and my friend,"},{"time":244130,"text":"and filmmaker and partner Sabaah Folayan"},{"time":246126,"text":"did just that with our documentary,"},{"time":248328,"text":"\"Whose Streets?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":251496,"text":"I kind of became a conduit"},{"time":253632,"text":"for all of this courage\nthat was given to me."},{"time":257178,"text":"And I think that's part\nof our job as artists."},{"time":261016,"text":"I think we should be conveyors\nof courage in the work that we do."},{"time":265334,"text":"And I think that we are the wall\nbetween the normal folks"},{"time":269640,"text":"and the people that use their power\nto spread fear and hate,"},{"time":273120,"text":"especially in times like these."}]},{"cues":[{"time":276437,"text":"So I'm going to ask you."},{"time":278262,"text":"Y'all the movers and the shakers,"},{"time":280550,"text":"you know, the thought leaders:"},{"time":282628,"text":"What are you gonna do"},{"time":284492,"text":"with the gifts that you've been given"},{"time":286539,"text":"to break us from the fear\nthe binds us every day?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":289760,"text":"Because, see, I'm afraid every day."},{"time":292484,"text":"I can't remember a time when I wasn't."},{"time":295306,"text":"But once I figured out that fear\nwas not put in me to cripple me,"},{"time":299573,"text":"it was there to protect me,"},{"time":301804,"text":"and once I figured out\nhow to use that fear,"},{"time":304824,"text":"I found my power."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307106,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308326,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}